description:
Tamers12345: First of all i'd like to thank each and every one of you for liking and watching my videos each week it means A lot to me and it's really what keeps me going. 2nd I would like to remind all of you to comment rate and subscribe!

Sonic: Hey what about me and Bartleby! Can we say something to Tamers?

Tamers12345: Haha! Of course you can!

Sonic: Thanks! Okay Bartleby. You may talk now. Presenting the great and rich... Bartleby Montclaire of Dresdin!

Bartleby: Thank you everyone for watchingTamers12345's videos. Hm hm. Of course. We all know the real reason you watch them is for me of course. You may carry on with your business now.

Manic: Wait! the rest of us want to say something!

Tamers12345: Sure Manic. Go ahead.

Tamers12345, Sonic, Manic, Sonia, Knuckles, Mindy, Bartleby, and Mindy's dad: HAPPY VALENTINES DAY EVERYONE! THANKS SO MUCH FOR BEING WITH US ALL THIS TIME!!!
creator: THOMAS BERGERSEN, ASCAP
